name: Searching Soul
description:
Inside myself is a place where I live all alone, and that's where I renew my springs that never dry up. 

I return to Kolukkumalai, Munnar, on a regular basis to refresh my spirits, seeking solitude and self-richness. I'm not sure how many times I've gone there, but I always make sure I don't miss the sunrise.

This is a self-portrait I took using my tripod.
